 serving bowl and gently stir to combine. Set aside."},{"content":"Place coconut milk and water into mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and weigh in rice. Remove simmering basket and rinse rice under cold water until water runs clear. Place simmering basket with rinsed rice into mixing bowl and cook <b>17 min\/Varoma\/speed 3<b>."},{"content":"Add peas and corn over rice in simmering basket and cook <b>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 3<b>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and transfer rice, peas and corn to large bowl with reserved salad. Stir rice and vegetables through salad. Serve warm or cold."}],"basicInfo":["easy","35m","1h","4 portions"]}